OL,3,CWhat's making tortillas controversial
OL,4,Cin the US?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Assistant Producer
OL,7,FSasha Kay
OL,9,FThe state of California has brought in
OL,10,Fa new law requiring that manufacturers
OL,11,Fadd folic acid to tortillas to
OL,12,Fdecrease birth defects in Latino
OL,13,Fbabies.
OL,15,FMany have welcomed the change, but
OL,16,Fsome are claiming the Californian
OL,17,Fstate government of over-interference
OL,18,Fand even "colonising" traditional
OL,19,FLatin American foods.
OL,21,FWhat is the law?
