OL,3,CWhat's making tortillas controversial
OL,4,Cin the US?
OL,6,FAs of 2026, manufacturers must add
OL,7,Ffolic acid to corn masa products sold
OL,8,Fin California.
OL,10,FCorn masa products are a staple of
OL,11,FLatin American cooking, and the most
OL,12,Fcommon is tortilla.
OL,14,FWhy has the law been brought in?
OL,16,FLocal government says its goal is to
OL,17,Fdecrease birth defects in children
OL,18,Fborn to Latina mothers.
