OL,3,CWhat's making tortillas controversial
OL,4,Cin the US?
OL,6,FCalifornia has the largest total
OL,7,FLatino population of any US state,
OL,8,Fwith almost 16 million people making
OL,9,Fup 40% of the state's residents.
OL,11,FWhy is it controversial?
OL,13,FTortillas have been made in the same
OL,14,Fway for several thousand years, using
OL,15,Fjust four ingredients: corn masa,
OL,16,Fwater, a fat, and salt.
