OL,6,FThis traditional recipe is entrenched
OL,7,Fin Latin American cooking, passed down
OL,8,Fthrough generations, and seen by some
OL,9,Fpeople as an important part of culture
OL,10,Fto protect.
OL,12,FEnrique Rodriguez, CEO of La
OL,13,FPrincesita Tortilleria tortilla
OL,14,Fcompany in Los Angeles, has been
OL,15,Fopposed to the law since its initial
OL,16,Fdraft.
OL,18,FIn 2024, he wrote an open letter to
OL,19,Fthe Senate Health Committee in an
OL,20,Feffort to postpone the initial
OL,21,Fhearings.
